    dc:creator "Başköse, İsa; Özüdoğru, Bariş; Savran, Ahmet; Keskin, Ali" ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Brassica (Brassicaceae) from Bolkar Mountains (Türkiye) with morphological and molecular evidence" ;
